high_descs: Turn left and face the sink in front of you.
Take the knife from the sink in front of you.
Turn right and face the sink to your left.
Slice the apple in the sink in front of you.
Place the knife in the sink in front of you.
Take an apple slice from the sink in front of you.
Turn around and face the microwave on top of the stove to your right.
Place the apple in the microwave, then take it out.
Turn right and face the fridge in front of you.
Place the apple in the fridge and close it.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the front of the sink.
Pick up the gray knife in the sink
Move over to the right side of the sink.
Cut the apple inside the sink into three parts.
Place the knife into he sink in front of the fork.
Pick up one piece of the apple.
Turn around and go to the microwave above the stove on the right.
Remove the apple after heating it next to another apple in the microwave.
Turn right to go to the front of the refrigerator.
Place the apple piece in the middle shelf of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated piece of apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the sink.
Pick up the knife from the sink.
Move to the right.
Cut the apple in the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of apple from the sink.
Turn around, go across the room, turn right and go to the stove.
Put the slice of apple in the microwave, cook it and pick it back up.
Turn to the right and head to the fridge.
Put the apple on the shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked sliced of apple in the fridge.
